<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2668016>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31A–E. Eupelmus confusus Al khatib. A–C, ♀. D–E, ♂. A, habitus. B, mesotarsus in lateroventral view. C, fore wing venation. D, habitus. E, fore wing venation. Female ex A. ramosus from Aléria, Vaccaja, Corse, France; male ex A. ramosus from Vizzini, Monte Iblei, Sicilia, Italy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2668016/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2668038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Trophic web of A. ramosus. Horizontal scale bars proportional to the numbers of reared specimens examined that are indicated in the bars. Arrows pointing out the direction of the trophic relationships: from phytophagous Bruchophagus spp. to the asphodel and from parasitoids to chalcid hosts. The estimated number of Bruchophagus abscedus parasitized by P. depilata was estimated considering that a mean of 10 Puklina emerge from a larva of Bruchophagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2668038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2668032>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Trophic web of A. albus albus. Horizontal scale bars proportional to the numbers of reared specimens examined that are indicated in the bars. Arrows pointing out the direction of the trophic relationships: from phytophagous Bruchophagus spp. to the asphodel and from parasitoids to chalcid hosts." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2668032/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

